    FormComponents.Form

    public class TestPrepForm
extends FormComponents
implements FormComponents.Form
    alias selected (actual) function to (formal) function in differential equation definition. this is a preparation for running the range of the equation to calculate the error. the error function is typically displayed or used to find the max error value.
    Author:
    Michael Druckman
